        <main class="container mx-auto relative">
            <section class="max-w-screen-lg mx-auto px-8 py-16 flex flex-wrap-reverse items-center">
                <div class="mt-16 md:mt-0 md:w-7/12">
                    <h1 class="font-bold text-gray-700 text-3xl md:text-4xl">Creating<br>
                        <span class="uppercase">
                            <span class="invisible">fast</span>
                            <span class="invisible">beautiful</span>
                            <span class="invisible">scalable</span>
                            <span class="invisible">optimized</span></span><br>websites is my expertise</h1>
                    <h2 class="mt-4 md:text-lg text-gray-700" :class="darkMode ? 'text-gray-400' : 'text-gray-700'">I am a full-stack web developer with a lot of passion for what i'm doing!</h2>
                    <nav class="mt-8 flex items-center">
                        <a href="#contact" class="text-sm px-4 py-3 rounded font-bold uppercase tracking-wide bg-green-500 text-white">Contact</a>
                        <a href="#projects" class="text-sm px-4 py-3 rounded font-bold uppercase tracking-wide bg-green-200 text-green-500 ml-4">Projects</a>
                    </nav>
                </div>
                <figure class="w-full md:w-5/12 md:pl-16"><img class="w-1/2 object-cover mx-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg md:w-full" src="assets/me.png" alt="A selfie of yours truly."></figure>
            </section>
            <section class="py-16 border-b-2 border-t-2 bg-gray-100" :class="darkMode ? 'bg-gray-900 border-gray-800' : 'bg-gray-100'">
                <div class="max-w-screen-lg mx-auto px-8">
                    <h3 class="font-bold leading-tight text-2xl md:text-3xl">What I do for a living.</h3>
                    <p class="mt-2 max-w-lg">Listed below you will find a comprehensive list of the skills and services that I provide for my clients.</p>
                    <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-16 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold">Accessibility</h4>
                            <p class="mt-2 text-sm">I am constantly making sure the code I produce is WCAG compliant and accessible to all users, regardless of their disabilities. Nobody should have a poor experience when it comes to the web.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold">Backend Development</h4>
                            <p class="mt-2 text-sm">I can build full-blown traditional content management systems with Craft CMS, or headless APIs for accessing and consuming data with Node and GraphQL.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold">Deployment</h4>
                            <p class="mt-2 text-sm">I am an expert at configuring continuous deployment and continuous integration. My tools of choice are DigitalOcean, Netlify, and GitHub Actions.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold">Frontend Development</h4>
                            <p class="mt-2 text-sm">My biggest strength is turning static mockups and designs into fully responsive codebases. I am proficient in the latest and greatest frontend frameworks like React, Vue, Svelte, and TailwindCSS.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold">Hosting</h4>
                            <p class="mt-2 text-sm">Regardless of project type, I can configure servers, domains, and credentials to make sure everything is secure, performant, and dead-simple.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold">Web Consulting</h4>
                            <p class="mt-2 text-sm">I can observe, diagnose, and recommend solutions in all of the services listed on this very page.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section>Timeline</section>
            <section>Project</section>
            <form name="contact" method="post" aria-label="contact form" action="/?contact" id="contact" class="max-w-screen-lg mx-auto px-8 py-16"><input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact">
                <div x-show="!submittedForm" class="max-w-lg">
                    <h3 class="font-bold leading-tight text-2xl md:text-3xl">Get in touch with me.</h3>
                    <p class="mt-2">Fill out the form below, and I'll be in contact as soon as possible. Thank you so much for taking the time to check me out.</p>
                </div>
                <div x-show="submittedForm" class="max-w-lg" style="display: none;">
                    <h3 class="font-bold leading-tight text-2xl md:text-3xl">Thank you for reaching out!</h3>
                    <p class="mt-2">I will be in touch very shortly, my friend.</p>
                </div>
                <div x-show="!submittedForm" class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-2 gap-8">
